#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:60
msgid "Keyboards"
msgstr "Tastature"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:63
msgid "Numpad Emulation"
msgstr "Simulacija numeričke tastature"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:65
msgid ""
"If you do not have a numeric Numpad on the side of your keyboard, you "
"may want to emulate one (uses the numbers at the top of the keyboard "
"instead, however, removes quick access to layer visibility)."
msgstr ""
"Ako posedujete računar bez numeričke tastature, možda želite da je "
"simulirate (koristi alfanumeričku tastaturu na račun brzog odabira "
"slojeva u sceni)."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:71
msgid ""
"Read more about *Numpad Emulation* in the :doc:`User Preferences </"
"preferences/input>`."
msgstr ""
"Pojašnjenje ćete naći u *Numpad Emulation* na :doc:`User Preferences </"
"preferences/input>`."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:75
msgid "Non-English Keyboards"
msgstr "Jezični raspored tastature"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:77
msgid ""
"If you use a keyboard with a non-English keyboard layout, you still may "
"benefit from switching your computer to the UK or US layout as long as "
"you work with Blender."
msgstr ""
"Ako koristite tastaturu čije su oznake, raspored i oblik tastera "
"prilagođeni konkretnom jeziku, možda ćete želeti da podesite sistemski "
"izbor rasporeda na \"UK\" ili \"US\" dok radite u Blenderu."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:82
msgid ""
"You can also change the default keymap and default hotkeys from the :doc:"
"`User Preferences </preferences/input>`, however, this manual assumes "
"you are using the default keymap."
msgstr ""
"Takođe možete odlučiti da izmenite podrazumevani raspored u Blenderu iz :"
"doc:`User Preferences </preferences/input>`, ali ovaj priručnik "
"pretpostavlja da niste menjali ovaj parametar."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:92
msgid ""
"Graphics tablets can be used to provide a more traditional method of "
"controlling the mouse cursor using a pen. This can help to provide a "
"more familiar experience for artists who are used to painting and "
"drawing with similar tools, as well as provide additional controls such "
"as pressure sensitivity."
msgstr ""
"Tableti za crtanje se koriste da pruže \"prirodniju\" metodu nišanjenja "
"kursorom uz pomoć specijalne olovke. Ovo pruža prepoznatljiv osećaj "
"umetnicima koji su navikli da crtaju i boje sličnim alatkama, a kao "
"dodatnu funkcionalnost, imate kontrolu i nad jačinom pritiska, i dr."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:99
msgid ""
"If you are using a graphic tablet instead of a mouse and pressure "
"sensitivity does not work properly, try to place the mouse pointer in "
"the Blender window and then unplug/replug your graphic tablet. This "
"might help."
msgstr ""
"Ako koristite tablet za crtanje umesto miša, a osetljivost na pritisak "
"ne daje adekvatan osećaj, probajte da pozicionirate kursor miša u okno "
"Blendera, a zatim da razvežete i povežete tablet; ovo možda pomogne."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:106
msgid "3D Mice"
msgstr "3D miševi"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:108
msgid ""
"3D Mice or :abbr:`NDOF (N-Degrees of Freedom)` devices are hardware that "
"you can use to navigate a scene in Blender. Currently only devices made "
"by 3Dconnexion are supported. These devices allow you to explore a "
"scene, as well as :ref:`Walk/Fly modes <3dview-walk-fly>`."
msgstr ""
"3D miševi, tj. :abbr:`NDOF (N-Degrees of Freedom)` uređaji su hardver "
"koji pomaže navigaciji kroz trodimenzionalnu \"scenu\" u Blenderu. Za "
"sada su podržani isključivo uređaji firme 3Dconnexion. Ovim uređajima "
"možete istražiti scenu na razne načine, npr. :ref:`Walk/Fly modes "
"<3dview-walk-fly>`."

