msgid ""
"See :doc:`Input Preference </preferences/input>` for more information on "
"configuring peripherals."
msgstr ""
"Vidi :doc:`Input Preference </preferences/input>` za dodatne informacije "
"o prilagođavanju perifernih uređaja."
